{"word":"ὅθεν","slug":"ὅθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὅϑεν</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pron.\">pron.</a> <el>ὅ</el> and source suffix -<el>ϑεν</el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a>, marker of derivation, <b>whence<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> spatially, <b>from where, whence <a href='B:470 12:44'>Mt 12:44</a>; <a href='B:470 25:24'>25:24</a>; <a href='B:490 11:24'>Lk 11:24</a>; <a href='B:510 28:13'>Ac 28:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of result, <b>as result of which, consequently <a href='B:470 14:7'>Mt 14:7</a>; <a href='B:510 14:26'>Ac 14:26</a>; <a href='B:510 26:19'>26:19</a>; <a href='B:650 2:17'>Hb 2:17</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Hb; <b><a href='B:690 2:18'>1 J 2:18</a></b> (of a deduction). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὄζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὀθόνη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}